The audience chamber is right above
here, but His Majesty the Emperor
is not here right now.

rows.label: tlk45320351_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If you seek an audience, please
return some other time.

rows.label: tlk45320351_01_msg00102
rows.name:
I regret to inform you that Emperor
Nefer is most busy with his official
duties at the present time.

rows.label: tlk45320351_01_msg00103
rows.name:
If you wish to see him, please
return another time.
